%F A077398 a(n) = 16*a(n-2) - a(n-4) + 7, n >= 3. [corrected by _Vladimir Pletser_, Feb 29 2020]
%F A077398 Let b(n) be A077397 then a(n+2) = 2*a(n+1) - a(n) + b(n) with a(0)=0 a(1)=2.
